SchemaItem.Name: 00020_MigrateExchangeRate
SchemaItem.M01:
-- pokud se predchozi datum Do nanajede, vloži se tam 01-01-1970
Update ExchangeRate set DateFrom = ISNULL(( select TOP 1 DateTo from ExchangeRate AS B where B.refCurrencyId = ExchangeRate.refCurrencyId and B.refExchangeRateListId = ExchangeRate.refExchangeRateListId and B.DateTo < ExchangeRate.DateTo order by B.DateTo DESC),'1970-01-01')
